name: The Bag Securer
imagePrompt: A glowing digital scroll unfurling, revealing a collage of Web3 symbols, crypto charts, and anime characters, all being 'collected' into a glowing satchel with a symbol. The scene is vibrant and futuristic.
abilityText: Draw 2 cards. 'Alpha leaked. Don't tell anyone.'
flavorText: Knows the roadmap. Knows the team. Knows the tokenomics. Still gonna ape in at the literal top.

spellEffect.description: "Collected! This is so cool!" Draw 2 cards. If you control a minion with 5 or more Attack, draw an additional card.
